 *     7  - I/O3 - TEC sense
 *     8  - I/O4 - TEC control 1
 *     9  - I/O5 - TEC control 2
 *     10 - I/O6 - TEC control 3
 *     11 - I/O7 - NC
 *
 * The VREF pin is connected to ground with a capacitor. */
